title: Paperfrenzy - Past Examination Papers
description: PaperFrenzy.in offers a high-quality collection of CBSE past papers, created by students for students. Built by Arnav Vinnakota and myself, we aim to provide a safe, reliable resource after being frustrated by low-quality or unsafe websites. With additional resources coming soon, PaperFrenzy.in is designed to help students and teachers prepare effectively for exams with ease and confidence.
